pull_request.body:
Since I needed to know how signatures would be listed in `generate.yml` for the interoperability tests, I decided to just finish all of the signature templating code.

I haven't added all the signatures yet. I'll do that along with the KEMS in one fell swoop. The separate commit adding `sphincs_haraka_128f_robust` was just done to test the templating mechanism.
